      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hugo Barreto is a PostDoc at Institut Cochin. His research interests focus eco-evolutionary dynamics of Escherichia coli in different environments, such as the Human gut microbiota. His currently main interest is leveraging the evolutionary paths taken by E. coli to understand how it can evade colonization resistance within the Human gut microbiota.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
